Package io.github.zero88.schedulerx

Interface ExecutionResult<OUTPUT>

Type Parameters:
OUTPUT - Type of execution result
public interface ExecutionResult<OUTPUT>
Represents for an execution result will be pass on each event of SchedulingMonitor
Since:
2.0.0
See Also:
  • SchedulingMonitor
API Note:
This interface is renamed from TaskResult since 2.0.0

      @Nullable <T> T externalId()
      Get the unique id in external system that is declared in JobData.externalId().
      Type Parameters:
      T - Type of external id
      Returns:
      the external id, it can be nullable
      API Note:
      The type of the external id must be the same as your declaration in JobData.externalId(). Please use the correct data type otherwise you may get ClassCastException at runtime.
